#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/2aLNp9HBPNj9mI5R2tFw4vcfbFL.jpg" group-title="|DE| KINDER FILME" tvg-type="movie" description="An endearing modern-day story about how the lovable Goof bonds with his teenage son Max on a hilarious cross-country road trip. En route to the ol' fishing hole, they find themselves up to their floppy ears in misadventure!" year="1995-04-07" director="Kevin Lima" actors="Bill Farmer, Jason Marsden, Rob Paulsen, Jim Cummings, Kellie Martin",A Goofy Movie (1995)
