#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/ode14q7WtDugFDp78fo9lCsmay9.jpg" group-title="|DE| FILME KOLLEKTION" tvg-type="movie" description="Set in a post-apocalyptic world, young Thomas is deposited in a community of boys after his memory is erased, soon learning they're all trapped in a maze that will require him to join forces with fellow “runners” for a shot at escape." year="2014-09-10" director="H.H. Cooper, Mirashyam Blakeslee, Vanessa Hickey, Wes Ball, Nancy Breaux" actors="Dylan O'Brien, Kaya Scodelario, Aml Ameen, Thomas Brodie-Sangster, Ki Hong Lee",DE - Maze Runner: Die Auserwählten im Labyrinth (2014)
