#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/vvk5aWBJE3EqDX2ln6M4J4UiUXr.jpg" group-title="|DE| FILME KOLLEKTION" tvg-type="movie" description="A new batch of recruits arrives at Police Academy, this time a group of civilian volunteers who have joined Commandant Lassard's new Citizens on Patrol program. Although the community relations project has strong governmental support, a disgusted Captain Harris is determined to see it fail." year="1987-04-02" director="Jim Drake, Michael Zenon, Elaine Yarish, M. James Arnett, Bill Bannerman" actors="Steve Guttenberg, Bubba Smith, Michael Winslow, David Graf, Tim Kazurinsky",DE - Police Academy 4: Und jetzt geht’s rund (1987)
