#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/gRFJ3xLewH1rwEplZBfKS4vGpFV.jpg" group-title="|DE| FILME KOLLEKTION" tvg-type="movie" description="Our favourite police men are called together to deal with a gang who rob banks and jewelers. Using their various talents as well as their extraordinary luck, the crooks stand no chance against our men and women in blue." year="1989-03-09" director="Peter Bonerz, Artist W. Robinson, Chuck Rowley, J. Ellen Evans, Marty P. Ewing" actors="Bubba Smith, David Graf, Michael Winslow, Leslie Easterbrook, Marion Ramsey",DE - Police Academy 6: Widerstand zwecklos (1989)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=351541.mkv&play_token=MgqXgrUa1l&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/m5a1U549gokC1kxsqgQoRb6XpFg.jpg" group-title="|DE| FILME KOLLEKTION" tvg-type="movie" description="New rules enforced by the Lady Mayoress mean that sex, weight, height and intelligence need no longer be a factor for joining the Police Force. This opens the floodgates for all and sundry to enter the Police Academy, much to the chagrin of the instructors. Not everyone is there through choice, though. Social misfit Mahoney has been forced to sign up as the only alternative to a jail sentence and it doesn't take long before he falls foul of the boorish Lieutenant Harris. But before long, Mahoney realises that he is enjoying being a police cadet and decides he wants to stay... while Harris decides he wants Mahoney out!" year="1984-03-22" director="Hugh Wilson, Penelope Hynam, Allan Harmon, Michael Zenon, Rocco Gismondi" actors="Steve Guttenberg, Kim Cattrall, G.W. Bailey, Bubba Smith, Donovan Scott",DE - Police Academy 7: Mission in Moskau (1994)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=351542.mkv&play_token=oJzmgJ52Yy&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/m5a1U549gokC1kxsqgQoRb6XpFg.jpg" group-title="|DE| FILME KOLLEKTION" tvg-type="movie" description="New rules enforced by the Lady Mayoress mean that sex, weight, height and intelligence need no longer be a factor for joining the Police Force. This opens the floodgates for all and sundry to enter the Police Academy, much to the chagrin of the instructors. Not everyone is there through choice, though. Social misfit Mahoney has been forced to sign up as the only alternative to a jail sentence and it doesn't take long before he falls foul of the boorish Lieutenant Harris. But before long, Mahoney realises that he is enjoying being a police cadet and decides he wants to stay... while Harris decides he wants Mahoney out!" year="1984-03-22" director="Hugh Wilson, Penelope Hynam, Allan Harmon, Michael Zenon, Rocco Gismondi" actors="Steve Guttenberg, Kim Cattrall, G.W. Bailey, Bubba Smith, Donovan Scott",DE - Police Academy: Dümmer als die Polizei erlaubt (1984)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=351536.mkv&play_token=s6gfcvS1Ji&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/vN5B5WgYscRGcQpVhHl6p9DDTP0.jpg" group-title="|DE| FILME KOLLEKTION" tvg-type="movie" description="Eighties teenager Marty McFly is accidentally sent back in time to 1955, inadvertently disrupting his parents' first meeting and attracting his mother's romantic interest. Marty must repair the damage to history by rekindling his parents' romance and - with the help of his eccentric inventor friend Doc Brown - return to 1985." year="1985-07-03" director="Robert Zemeckis, Pamela M. Eilerson, David McGiffert, Frank Marshall" actors="Michael J. Fox, Christopher Lloyd, Crispin Glover, Lea Thompson, Claudia Wells",DE - Zurück in die Zukunft (1985)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=351535.mkv&play_token=YQwja06pyB&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/YBawEsTkUZBDajKbd5LiHkmMGf.jpg" group-title="|DE| FILME KOLLEKTION" tvg-type="movie" description="Marty and Doc are at it again as the time-traveling duo head to 2015 to nip some McFly family woes in the bud. But things go awry thanks to bully Biff Tannen and a pesky sports almanac. In a last-ditch attempt to set things straight, Marty finds himself bound for 1955 and face to face with his teenage parents -- again." year="1989-11-22" director="Robert Zemeckis, David McGiffert, Marion Tumen, Cara Giallanza, Max Kleven" actors="Michael J. Fox, Christopher Lloyd, Lea Thompson, Thomas F. Wilson, Elisabeth Shue",DE - Zurück in die Zukunft II (1989)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=351533.mkv&play_token=13b1TFP3X7&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/crzoVQnMzIrRfHtQw0tLBirNfVg.jpg" group-title="|DE| FILME KOLLEKTION" tvg-type="movie" description="The final installment finds Marty digging the trusty DeLorean out of a mineshaft and looking for Doc in the Wild West of 1885. But when their time machine breaks down, the travelers are stranded in a land of spurs. More problems arise when Doc falls for pretty schoolteacher Clara Clayton, and Marty tangles with Buford Tannen." year="1990-05-25" director="Robert Zemeckis, David McGiffert, Cara Giallanza, Carla Corwin, Batan Silva" actors="Michael J. Fox, Christopher Lloyd, Mary Steenburgen, Thomas F. Wilson, Lea Thompson",DE - Zurück in die Zukunft III (1990)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=351534.mkv&play_token=3T8tbq82ak&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/l5uxY5m5OInWpcExIpKG6AR3rgL.jpg" group-title="|DE| FILME KOLLEKTION" tvg-type="movie" description="When Ethan Hunt, the leader of a crack espionage team whose perilous operation has gone awry with no explanation, discovers that a mole has penetrated the organization, he's surprised to learn that he's the prime suspect. To clear his name, Hunt now must ferret out the real double agent and, in the process, even the score." year="1996-05-22" director="Brian De Palma, Diana Dill, Chris Soldo, Nick Moore, Eric Schwab" actors="Tom Cruise, Jon Voight, Emmanuelle Béart, Henry Czerny, Jean Reno",DE - Mission: Impossible (1996)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=351527.mkv&play_token=2Ma1NlhurT&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/AkJQpZp9WoNdj7pLYSj1L0RcMMN.jpg" group-title="|DE| FILME KOLLEKTION" tvg-type="movie" description="When an IMF mission ends badly, the world is faced with dire consequences. As Ethan Hunt takes it upon himself to fulfill his original briefing, the CIA begin to question his loyalty and his motives. The IMF team find themselves in a race against time, hunted by assassins while trying to prevent a global catastrophe." year="2018-07-13" director="Sarah Mooney, Christopher McQuarrie, Gabrielle Mankiewicz, Nicoletta Mani, Wade Eastwood" actors="Tom Cruise, Henry Cavill, Ving Rhames, Simon Pegg, Rebecca Ferguson",DE - Mission: Impossible: Fallout (2018)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=351528.mkv&play_token=50Bw71JDFs&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/sGvcWcI99OTXLzghD7qXw00KaY5.jpg" group-title="|DE| FILME KOLLEKTION" tvg-type="movie" description="Ethan and team take on their most impossible mission yet—eradicating 'The Syndicate', an International and highly-skilled rogue organization committed to destroying the IMF." year="2015-07-23" director="Christopher McQuarrie, Lisa Vick, Toby Hefferman, Tommy Gormley, Karima Guennouni" actors="Tom Cruise, Jeremy Renner, Simon Pegg, Rebecca Ferguson, Ving Rhames",DE - Mission: Impossible: Rogue Nation (2015)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=351532.mkv&play_token=6N5UlU7Zud&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/7us8nE3ldE0gX2cziUz4tKg0Go0.jpg" group-title="|DE| FILME KOLLEKTION" tvg-type="movie" description="With computer genius Luther Stickell at his side and a beautiful thief on his mind, agent Ethan Hunt races across Australia and Spain to stop a former IMF agent from unleashing a genetically engineered biological weapon called Chimera. This mission, should Hunt choose to accept it, plunges him into the center of an international crisis of terrifying magnitude." year="2000-05-24" director="John Woo, Randi Feldman, Judy Whitehead, Kristin Voumard, William H. Burton Sr." actors="Tom Cruise, Dougray Scott, Thandiwe Newton, Ving Rhames, Richard Roxburgh",DE - Mission: Impossible II (2000)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=351529.mkv&play_token=mOJIvoI1Cb&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/vKGYCpmQyV9uHybWDzXuII8Los5.jpg" group-title="|DE| FILME KOLLEKTION" tvg-type="movie" description="Retired from active duty, and training recruits for the Impossible Mission Force, agent Ethan Hunt faces the toughest foe of his career: Owen Davian, an international broker of arms and information, who's as cunning as he is ruthless. Davian emerges to threaten Hunt and all that he holds dear – including the woman Hunt loves." year="2006-04-25" director="J.J. Abrams, Brad Arnold, Inti Carboni, Velvet Andrews-Smith, Jia Ji Cheng" actors="Tom Cruise, Philip Seymour Hoffman, Ving Rhames, Billy Crudup, Michelle Monaghan",DE - Mission: Impossible III (2006)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=351530.mkv&play_token=jWDU4gQRMM&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/eRZTGx7GsiKqPch96k27LK005ZL.jpg" group-title="|DE| FILME KOLLEKTION" tvg-type="movie" description="Ethan Hunt and his team are racing against time to track down a dangerous terrorist named Hendricks, who has gained access to Russian nuclear launch codes and is planning a strike on the United States. An attempt to stop him ends in an explosion causing severe destruction to the Kremlin and the IMF to be implicated in the bombing, forcing the President to disavow them. No longer being aided by the government, Ethan and his team chase Hendricks around the globe, although they might still be too late to stop a disaster." year="2011-12-07" director="Brad Bird, Prince Shah, Jakub Dvorak, Raj Acharya, Udayan Baijal" actors="Tom Cruise, Paula Patton, Simon Pegg, Jeremy Renner, Michael Nyqvist",DE - Mission: Impossible IV: Phantom Protokoll (2011)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=351531.mkv&play_token=9jfGOyxAIO&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/7RwHxhdUNS996JPFNB9a7CJtlwR.jpg" group-title="|DE| FILME KOLLEKTION" tvg-type="movie" description="Law enforcement finds itself chasing the ghost of a man dead for over a decade, embroiled in a diabolical new game that's only just begun." year="2017-10-25" director="Michael Spierig, Peter Spierig, Ryan Jakubek, Lawrence Ng, Bianca Marini" actors="Matt Passmore, Tobin Bell, Callum Keith Rennie, Hannah Emily Anderson, Clé Bennett",DE - Jigsaw (2017)
http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=351520.mkv&play_token=j6K4V9pVbN&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/4da0TS3iQ1IzuyhDS8elgkmOfrN.jpg" group-title="|DE| FILME KOLLEKTION" tvg-type="movie" description="Two men wake up to find themselves shackled in a grimy, abandoned bathroom. As they struggle to comprehend their predicament, they discover a disturbing tape left behind by the sadistic mastermind known as Jigsaw. With a chilling voice and cryptic instructions, Jigsaw informs them that they must partake in a gruesome game in order to secure their freedom." year="2004-10-01" director="James Wan, Daniel J. Heffner, Jillian Giacomini, Alexa Sheehan" actors="Cary Elwes, Leigh Whannell, Danny Glover, Monica Potter, Ken Leung",DE - Saw I (2004)
