#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/f7JAX5EGk4GgsEnus6OxyzwpFp7.jpg" group-title="|DE| FILME KOLLEKTION" tvg-type="movie" description="Laurie Strode comes to her final confrontation with Michael Myers, the masked figure who has haunted her since she narrowly escaped his killing spree on Halloween night four decades ago." year="2018-10-18" director="Max Sturgeon, Atilla Salih Yücer, Kamen Velkovsky, David Gordon Green" actors="Jamie Lee Curtis, Judy Greer, Andi Matichak, James Jude Courtney, Nick Castle",DE - Halloween: Stelle dich deinem Schicksal (2018)
