http://mag.greatott.me:80/play/movie.php?mac=00:1A:79:74:B1:B9&stream=350245.mkv&play_token=O9SuwRd3Nf&type=movie&dummy=/movie/&type=movie

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/nsmW28GcNabCUZfP5YtUEe8Li0f.jpg" group-title="|DE| FILME KOLLEKTION" tvg-type="movie" description="The film that brings back horror icon Freddy Krueger as a darker and more sinister character than ever before. While Freddy is on the prowl, a group of teenagers being stalked soon learn they all have a common factor making them targets for this twisted killer." year="2010-04-30" director="Samuel Bayer, Kristin Bree Calabrese, Samantha C. Kirkeby, Ana Maria Quintana, Sharron Reynolds-Enriquez" actors="Jackie Earle Haley, Kyle Gallner, Rooney Mara, Katie Cassidy, Thomas Dekker",DE - A Nightmare on Elm Street (2010)
